{"lemma":"جُمْلَة","slug":"جُمْلَة","root":"ج.م.ل","root_slug":"ج-م-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"جُمْلَة","root":"جمل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6348"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%8F%D9%85%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"series, whole range, collectivity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"sentence","examples":[{"text":"اُكْتُبْ جُمْلَةً وَاحِدَةً.","english":"Write one sentence."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/d͡ʒum.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6348","headword_ar":"جُمْلَةٌ","root":"jml","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A strand"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thick rope: pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumolN","text_ar":"جُمْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"many strands"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a rope,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put together"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to compose a cable:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jum~alN","text_ar":"جُمَّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA, in two places in this art.) ―         -b2-  Hence, app., (TA,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aggregate"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a thing; (K;) the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sum, whole,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"total;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL, PS;) it implies muchness, or numerousness, and means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any aggregate unseparated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumalN","text_ar":"جُمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumolapN mino maAlK","text_ar":"جُمْلَةٌ مِنْ مَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"generally means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large sum of money;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and in a similar sense"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumolapN","text_ar":"جُمْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is often used in relation to various things.] It is said in the Kur [xxv. 34],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaAla A@l~a*iyna kafaruwA lawo laA nuz~ila Ealayohi","text_ar":"وَقَالَ ا@لَّذِينَ كَفَرُوا لَوْ لَا نُزِّلَ عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A@loquroA=nu jumolapF waAHidapF","text_ar":"ا@لْقُرْا=نُ جُمْلَةً وَاحِدَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e., ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And those who disbelieved said, Wherefore was not the Kur-án sent down,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"revealed, to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"aggregated?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) [or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in one aggregate?"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at once?"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd.) [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAljumolapi","text_ar":"بِالجُمْلَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Upon the whole; to sum up."},{"kind":"text","text":"] ―         -b3-  And hence, in grammar, (TA,) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A proposition; a clause; a phrase;"},{"kind":"text","text":"sometimes,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sentence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a phrase composed of a subject and an attribute,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"composed of an inchoative and an enunciative,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in which case it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumolapN A@somiy~apN","text_ar":"جُمْلَةٌ ا@سْمِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a verb and its agent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(in which case it is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jumolapN fiEoliy~apN","text_ar":"جُمْلَةٌ فِعْلِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)] (KT, TA,) [&c.,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether affording a complete sense,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zayodN qaAy^imN","text_ar":"زَيْدٌ قَايِمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[Zeyd is standing], or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ino yukorimoniY","text_ar":"اـِنْ يُكْرِمْنِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[If he treat me with honour]. (KT.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","KT"]}]}}